data.meta_description: Famous Writers - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a list of famous writers throughout history, including their dates and notable works. It covers over 100 authors from William Shakespeare in the 16th century to contemporary writers like George R.R. Martin. The writers came from several countries and wrote in different genres, such as plays, novels, poems, children's books, and more. Overall it serves as a who's who of influential authors through the centuries.
